flowRoot.flowPara: Folamour VR is a 3D multiplayer online game
using the Oculus Rift. Using his virtual reality device,
one of the players controls "missiles" with the sole power of his head movements. His goal is to prevent the other players from reaching the red flag located at the other end of the map...
This project uses the Oculus Rift, WebGL (through three.js), WebRTC and HTML5 audio technologies. It was developed mostly with Javascript, and the open source programs Gimp and Blender.

Using the Oculus Rift provides a very fun and immersive game experience for the player. Being able to play "handless", in the air, is a very unique sensation. Moreover, the game is playable online using any modern web browser.
